Inheritance is the Inheriting the properties of patient to child class is called Inheritance


1. Single Inheritance
2. Multilevel Inheritance
3. Hieratical Inheritance


Point Notes : Constructor is not inheritance , and Private modifiers not Inheritance


Advantage Of Inharitance : Reusable Code

Disadvantage : Titly Coupled (If we change in parent class that time we need to change the all sub class)


The Parent Class is Object class and the Kotlin class is the Any


